text: Michelle Franssen (born 14 December 1994) is a Belgian Paralympic swimmer who competes in international level events. She was a finalist in three of her events at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Ostend Category:Paralympic swimmers of Belgium Category:Belgian female swimmers Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Paralympics
